lines.text: have faith in me,
'cause there are things
that i've seen i don't believe.
so cling to what you know
and never let go.
you should know
things aren't always what they seem.
i said i'd never let you go and i never did.
i said i'd never let you fall
and i always meant it.
if you didn't have a chance then i never did.
you'll always find me right there again.
i'm going crazy,

i don't believe.
so we'll pretend it's alright
and stay in for the night.
